data.description: Amazing renovation opportunity in the historic Country Club neighborhood of Edina! This Tudor home has had the same owner for 38 years. Gorgeous hardwood floors and Italian marble tile flooring highlight the main level, along with a formal dining, living room, a study and powder room. Spacious upper level primary suite with large walk-in closet.  Attic is available to be finished for in-law suite or bonus room.  Walking distance to 50th/France shops and restaurants. Truly an exceptional location and opportunity!
